I"¹<h1 id="gaya-jekyll-theme">Gaya Jekyll Theme</h1>

<p>Modern responsive theme made for jekyll blogging platform. Gaya is a
simple theme build from ground up with the focus of performance. The
theme itself quickly adapts to the users device, so it looks great on
smartphones, tablets, desktops or even the large monitors.</p>

<ul>
  <li>Ability to change theme color at any time with any color.</li>
  <li>Easy customizable menu navigation.</li>
  <li>SEO Friendly.</li>
  <li>Embed image, YouTube/Vimeo video or SoundCloud audio to your post.</li>
</ul>

